<%= link_to image_tag("icons/fill/arrow-go-back-fill.png"), posts_path %>

<h2>New post</h2>
<p>Create a topic to be reviewed. Make sure to describe it neutrally as to not influence reviews.</p>
<p>All posts start with a rating of 5 and are averaged over every review.</p>

<%= form_with model: @post, url: "/posts", class: "styledform" do |f| %>
  <%= render "form", rating: 50, submittext: "Create Post", form: f %>
<% end %>
